| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3383 — Recovery Inhibition (blacklock)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0f5784fd-cdb7-5831-aab0-7e8ab6253d44"
